  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blue Hunter is a roguelike deckbuilding game with RPG elements. Fight monsters and revive them, level up, choose your stats, create your deck of undead monsters, beat gods and become the almighty god!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic stats: Choose which stats to increase with each level up. Create your own playstyle!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992190/extras/d78339386745a8b859d8f2621fc9093e.poster.avif?t=1739890214\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992190/extras/d78339386745a8b859d8f2621fc9093e.webm?t=1739890214\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992190/extras/d78339386745a8b859d8f2621fc9093e.mp4?t=1739890214\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strategic sacrifices: Are you ready to go through hell? Make sacrifices in order to get stronger. Only pain awaits you!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992190/extras/031d07fd5dd06306e41817a2b128f5aa.poster.avif?t=1739890214\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992190/extras/031d07fd5dd06306e41817a2b128f5aa.webm?t=1739890214\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992190/extras/031d07fd5dd06306e41817a2b128f5aa.mp4?t=1739890214\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An ever changing army: You can revive all the monsters you kill to assist you in battle as cards. Your deck is always unique!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992190/extras/93c6f8d3b65ce88a0c868b21d7bb3e5a.poster.avif?t=1739890214\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992190/extras/93c6f8d3b65ce88a0c868b21d7bb3e5a.webm?t=1739890214\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992190/extras/93c6f8d3b65ce88a0c868b21d7bb3e5a.mp4?t=1739890214\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
